high_descs: Go forward to the sink.
Pick up the yellow knife on the right front edge of the sink.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator.
Cut the apple inside the refrigerator into three parts.
Turn left and go back to the sink.
Place the knife on the counter on the right of the sink.
Turn around and go back to the refrigerator.
Take out one piece of the cut apple.
Move over left to the counter with the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave in front of the white cup and take it out.
Turn right and go to the white table on the left.
Place the apple piece on the table in front of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Move a heated piece of apple from the refrigerator to the table.

high_descs: Go to the sink
Pick up the knife
Go to the fridge
Cut the apple in the fridge
Go to the right of the sink
Put the knife down on the counter
Go to the fridge
Take an apple slice
Go to the microwave
Heat the apple slice
Go to the white table
Put the apple on the white table
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple slice on a table

high_descs: Head straight to the sink.
Pick up the knife in front of the sink.
Turn around and head to the fridge on your left.
Open the fridge and cut up the apple on the top shelf.
Turn left and head back to the sink.
Put the knife on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn around and head back to the fridge on your left.
Take a piece of apple out of the fridge.
Move to the microwave on your left.
Put the apple in the microwave in front of the cup and warm it up for a few seconds and then remove it again.
Turn right and move to the white three tier table on your left.
Put the apple on t he table in front of the green sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple on the top shelf of the white three tier table.
